snippet.title: PlayM2M- Administrator Level Gameplay Analysis and M2M E-Sports Arena
snippet.description:
https://discord.gg/playm2m and https://forum.playm2m.com

The damage and defense you see in this video are not representative of the original game for mechanics and gameplay demonstration only.!

NOTE: The game characters used in the video were created for analysis. The characters have a GOD trait that allows for disproportionate power damage and was only implemented for this video. The purpose of the video is to provide high quality gameplay. 

In the video content, M2M has entered the specialized e-Sports arena. We believe you will enjoy it!
